Package jx.classfile

Class Opcodes

java.lang.Object
jx.classfile.Opcodes
public final class Opcodes extends Object
This class contains all Java Virtual Machine Instruction. see http://java.sun.com/docs/books/vmspec/2nd-edition/html/Instructions.doc.html for details.
